room_title: Escape room "Escape from Mars" by ESCAPEability in Las Vegas

room_description: The NASA lost contact with all of the previous missions sent to Mars. Your unit has been selected to try another launch. They suspect that there might be some intelligent life forms on the red planet... Are you brave enough to figure that out for yourself?
